Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many jellyfish are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the jellyfish upside-down on its mushroom-like cap?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
